Resolved,
That the Orders made by the Secretary of State for the Home Department under the Sunday Entertainments Act, 1932, extending section 1 of the Act to—


(1) the City of Salford; 

(2) the City of Wells, in the County of Somerset; 

(3) the Borough of Crewe; 

(4) the Borough of Crosby; and

(5) the Borough of Sudbury

copies of which were presented to this House on 9th September, be approved."—[Mr. Peake.]
